{"tid":1124723,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"依家先知now原來咁多猁撚","createTime":"2019-04-25T08:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T08:09:21.000Z","uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6bdc895c1fc025a894ce60204b6d60dbed6b5e65","tid":1124723,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:00:58.000Z","msg":"出埋啲戇鳩分析幻想曼城最後三場有機會失分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【話題】季尾甩轆有前科 曼城冇甩拖？<br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports-體育】曼徹斯特打吡過後，曼城以1分壓倒利物浦，爭標手執主動權，但英超歷來發生過多次臨近衝線脫腳的事件，不時出現令人意外的戰果。曼城，真的坐定笠六？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【拆局】兩護級隊可阻藍月？<br />\n<br />\n到了最後一輪，曼城作客白禮頓倒可能是最艱難，因後者此刻尚未護級成功，問題是到了煞科的時候又可能已登安全島。不然，屆時一隊爭標、一隊護級，將會繼兩軍於本月初在英足盃交鋒（曼城小勝1:0）後，再次上演一場「盃賽」。<br />\n<br />\n相對而言，利物浦的餘下賽序更易打，除了煞科戰主場面對「搶7」的狼隊外，另外兩隊戰意並不鮮明，有條件全勝。所以，曼城始終不容有失。<br />\n<br />\n唔該你地班編輯現實啲啦 利物浦今季已經無左英超架啦 清醒吓好無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cea312c1f104fcd0747a208447251dab97a80c","tid":1124723,"uid":15745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:02:29.000Z","msg":"猁榮基"},{"pid":"0d8efeccb624ef8e4a3db48903a226a561057d29","tid":1124723,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20cea312c1f104fcd0747a208447251dab97a80c","tid":1124723,"uid":15745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:02:29.000Z","msg":"猁榮基"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:06:34.000Z","msg":"仲有做咩"},{"pid":"8ad77e548cf5fad68aea457fe2e9ef67ac2363a0","tid":1124723,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:09:21.000Z","msg":"陳祉俊"}]}